1. The study involves a group I.
2. The preoperative corneal NV area in group I was 8.75 ± 4.33%.
3. The corneal NV area in group I decreased to 5.62 ± 3.86% one week after the injection.
4. The corneal NV area in group I further decreased to 6.35 ± 3.02% one month after the injection.
5. The decrease in corneal NV area one week after the injection was statistically significant (p = 0.012).
6. The decrease in corneal NV area one month after the injection was also statistically significant (p = 0.012).
